  "contentHtml": "\n    \n    \n                \n                            \n                            <p>The 100,000‑sq‑ft lab which marks the Group’s expansion into diagnostic services supports 15 diagnostic disciplines and more than 3,500 test modalities, covering preventive, routine and specialised testing.\n                        </p>\n                \n            \n    \n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Teena Thacker\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Teena Thacker</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675387/ET-Bureau\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ET Bureau</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Feb 24, 2026 at 07:42 AM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                            <li>\n                                                        \n                                                            \n                                                                Read by \n                                                            \n                                                            100 Professionals\n                                                        \n                                                    </li>\n                                                                                    </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>Mumbai: <a href=\"/tag/torrent+group\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Torrent Group</a> on Monday said it has entered into the <a href=\"/tag/diagnostics+market\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">diagnostics market</a> with the launch of Torrent Diagnostics and the opening of India’s largest <a href=\"/tag/national+reference+laboratory\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">National Reference Laboratory</a> in Navi Mumbai, the company claimed.The 100,000‑sq‑ft lab which marks the Group’s expansion into <a href=\"/tag/diagnostic+services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">diagnostic services</a> supports 15 diagnostic disciplines and more than 3,500 test modalities, covering preventive, routine and specialised testing. <!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->The testing services include molecular diagnostics, genomics, digital pathology, microbiology, immunology, transplant-related testing and infectious disease workflows, it said. \n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        “Diagnostics is a discipline where trust is built through process integrity, scientific depth and consistency over time. As Torrent enters the diagnostics space, we have approached this business with a long-term perspective, starting with a strong scientific foundation. <!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->Anchoring the organisation around a <a href=\"/tag/national+reference+laboratory\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">national reference laboratory</a> allows us to offer one of the widest test menus in the industry as well as define strong governance structures, validation frameworks and quality standards,” said Varun Mehta, Director at <a href=\"/tag/torrent+group\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Torrent Group</a>.The company said that the laboratory offers one of the most extensive test menus in the country, supported by advanced capabilities such as Next Generation Sequencing, MALDI-TOF, BSL-3 containment and the first Transmission Electron Microscope in a standalone diagnostics lab in Western India”. <!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->The National Reference Laboratory is staffed by a highly skilled and experienced scientific and technical team, with domain leadership across disciplines to ensure rigour, compliance and continuous quality assurance, it further said.                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Teena Thacker</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Teena Thacker</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675387/ET-Bureau\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ET Bureau</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Feb 24, 2026 at 07:42 AM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Feb 24, 2026 at 07:42 AM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figur